<item>
            <title>[HIVE-8218] function registry shared across sessions in HiveServer2</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-8218</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;FunctionRegistry.mFunctions is static. That mean that in HS2 case, all users will have same set of valid udfs. Ie, add/delete temporary function by one user would affect the namespace of other users.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
